{"type":"message","id":"f71fc141","parentId":"7f3f836f","timestamp":"2026-03-28T08:04:16.008Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"skills 目录在 /home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/ 下。让我读取 miaoda-web-search 的 SKILL.md。","thinkingSignature":"e15f89510e7af4d972f774d9c2bc6b9b678e710477ee638c9770823947d768e1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uzoulqtu1hex_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1481,"output":72,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45534,"cost":{"input":0.00044429999999999996,"output":0.0000864,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018501299999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774685053306}}
{"type":"message","id":"67ad1ffc","parentId":"f71fc141","timestamp":"2026-03-28T08:04:16.014Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_uzoulqtu1hex_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774685056010}}
{"type":"message","id":"aa1fd635","parentId":"67ad1ffc","timestamp":"2026-03-28T08:04:24.108Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，现在我使用这个工具搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态。让我搜索几个关键词：\n\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态 2026\n2. 智能安防行业动态 2026\n3. IT运维服务趋势 2026\n4. 网络系统集成行业动态\n\n让我并行搜索这些关键词。","thinkingSignature":"9b74a0e721cd66bcf62b1ca95674ffa1957310e9989f5f16fcac2ad81a7f2201"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ucxu4t7369o1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型最新动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ucxu4t7369o1_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ucxu4t7369o1_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务发展趋势 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ucxu4t7369o1_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成行业动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2068,"output":295,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46344,"cost":{"input":0.0006204,"output":0.000354,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00229383}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774685056013}}
